 padding-top: 0px"><a href="http://hughsung.com/images/test/UnpackingtheMTNA2009ExhibitorsConvention_E00F/IMG_14498x6.JPG" title="Lester, SoYoung and me at the AirTurn MTNA Exhibition booth" rel="thumbnail"><img border="0" src="http://hughsung.com/images/test/UnpackingtheMTNA2009ExhibitorsConvention_E00F/IMG_1449.png" width="480" height="427" /></a></div>  <p></p>  <div class="wlWriterEditableSmartContent" id="scid:8747F07C-CDE8-481f-B0DF-C6CFD074BF67:a5a80709-09d1-4d6d-8c28-d260b4203dcf" style="padding-right: 0px; display: inline; padding-left: 0px; float: none; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px"><a href="http://hughsung.com/images/test/UnpackingtheMTNA2009ExhibitorsConvention_E00F/IMG_14508x6.JPG" title="Another view of the AirTurn Team!" rel="thumbnail"><img border="0" src="http://hughsung.com/images/test/UnpackingtheMTNA2009ExhibitorsConvention_E00F/IMG_1450.png" width="460" height="389" /></a></div>  <div class="wlWriterEditableSmartContent" id="scid:8747F07C-CDE8-481f-B0DF-C6CFD074BF67:8aa1e2dc-0c09-44af-b176-c71df72488e6" style="padding-right: 0px; display: inline; padding-left: 0px; float: none; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px"><a href="http://hughsung.com/images/test/UnpackingtheMTNA2009ExhibitorsConvention_E00F/IMG_14518x6.JPG" title="Closeup of the AirTurn table, featuring a netbook on a laptop stand and an HP Tablet PC, both running MusicReader" rel="thumbnail"><img border="0" src="http://hughsung.com/images/test/UnpackingtheMTNA2009ExhibitorsConvention_E00F/IMG_1451.png" width="460" height="424" /></a></div>  <div class="wlWriterEditableSmartContent" id="scid:8747F07C-CDE8-481f-B0DF-C6CFD074BF67:a5cf3189-b669-40b1-8e85-496ba2d2487d" style="padding-right: 0px; display: inline; padding-left: 0px; float: none; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px"><a href="http://hughsung.com/images/test/UnpackingtheMTNA2009ExhibitorsConvention_E00F/IMG_14538x6.JPG" title="Lookee here!  A celebrity picture together with the